name: King without a crown/Rei sem coroa
description: This NFT is the result of two physical works in the series "Corona-se" (Coroe-se) - Morphic Resonance, started in July 2020 when I found my crown. This year (2021) I found another crown on the street ... Am I waiting for my king? Does he exist? The word "Coroa" comes from the Latin "corona" and in Brazilian Portuguese "Coroa"
